{"tid":37061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【美國世紀】不賣給中企 飛利浦部份照明業務賣給美私","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:10:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T12:01:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c881fed3ce2377272dde48573fe767cba6d4ebd1","tid":37061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.technews.tw/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/12195041/2016-12-12_195007.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.technews.tw%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2F12195041%2F2016-12-12_195007.png&h=8b1c461d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n荷蘭皇家飛利浦電子（Royal Philips）稍早宣布，旗下 LED 照明零組件與汽車照明廠 Lumileds 的 80.1 ％股權，將售予美國私募投資公司阿波羅全球管理（Apollo Global Management, LLC.），交易金額約 20 億美元，而飛利浦則持有其餘 19.9 ％股權。 <br />\n<br />\n飛利浦在 2015 年拆分旗下 LED 照明零組件事業部及汽車照明事業部，將兩者整合為獨立公司 Lumileds 後，原計劃將 80.1 ％股權賣給中國金沙江創投（GSR Ventures）所主導的 Go Scale Capital，未料卻遭美國海外投資委員會（CFIUS）以「未預期隱憂」為由攔阻。飛利浦與 CFIUS 進行交涉後仍無法獲得核可，遂於 2016 年 1 月宣布與金沙江等投資方終止交易，並重新尋找買主，進一步與潛在買主洽談協商。 <br />\n<br />\n日前《彭博》（Bloomberg）報導披露，飛利浦正與阿波羅全球管理公司洽談有關交易，而阿波羅也是最有機會出線的買主。如今結果揭曉，飛利浦今（12）日稍早發布聲明表示，阿波羅以約莫 20 億美元資金購得 Lumileds 80.1 ％股權，預計將於 2017 年上半年完成交易。 <br />\n<br />\n該交易金額相較於先前 Go Scale Capital 的交易估值 33 億美元，確實有些許差距，但對於經歷交易破局的 Lumileds 而言，耽擱多時的出售案總算覓得合適賣家，相信將能為日後發展產生正面效益。飛利浦執行長 Frans van Houten 對阿波羅入主 Lumileds 感到相當滿意，他表示，該交易不僅為公司產品轉型完成重要一步，也讓 Lumileds 具備有利條件，在既有技術、創新與客戶群等優勢上持續成長並創造價值。 <br />\n<br />\n（首圖來源：達志影像）"},{"pid":"8413b5a04fc4b84b0af8272d56e8b233dd79d4a5","tid":37061,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b1fdd3a255f16b24ab9d8cb285474628607e61e","tid":37061,"uid":32204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"Trump : We are going to make America strong again<br />\nWe are going to make America safe again<br />\nWe are going to make America great again<br />\nWe are going to win, win, win and win !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8035ea0929ce5e018d547ca11cbf3bd0795c167e","tid":37061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:06:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf3a2894a5eff650a18b0a8355aa0dc0ef4d2c0","tid":37061,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:38:36.000Z","msg":"風叔呢"},{"pid":"9dc8765082fb7628699a2b1034de347cf150359b","tid":37061,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"世界一面倒吹抗共之風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee35018107b46b19dd1cad937b851ce0f84ad9df","tid":37061,"uid":18381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T08:49:20.000Z","msg":"若要生活好........"},{"pid":"cdc01ddea8d3217f8a37f7a345ee9466eed57f40","tid":37061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e359cf6d784708a5d9e7155ed930df0e33f92cb","tid":37061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T11:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40bf12b80ca2e6eb8cb9fec0c4c1c6da1cdcf5d","tid":37061,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}